i   aren't working on the host. They're captured by the VM. Press Left		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   Ctrl + Right Ctrl to return control to the host. Press again to		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   control the VM.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   Now we can disable the keyboard and mouse relay of Looking Glass.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   Create `/etc/looking-glass-client.ini` with the following content:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     [spice]		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     enable=no		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
